---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us" description="Learn about Scandic Roots — our mission, India training alliance, and 5-stage vetting process connecting Indian talent with German employers.">

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  HERO — Split-screen with floating stats
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="ab-hero">
  <div class="ab-hero__left">
    <div class="ab-hero__left-inner">
      <div class="ab-hero__eyebrow">
        <span class="dot"></span>
        <p>Sweden-Based. India-Sourced. Germany-Focused.</p>
      </div>
      <h1 class="ab-hero__title">
        We Bridge<br />
        <em>Two Worlds.</em>
      </h1>
      <p class="ab-hero__sub">Scandic Roots was built to solve Germany's growing skilled labor shortage by creating a structured, ethical, and results-driven bridge between Indian workforce talent and German employers.</p>
      <div class="ab-hero__btns">
        <a href="/services" class="btn-glow">Explore Our Programs <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-ghost">Contact Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ab-hero__right">
    <div class="ab-hero__map-bg">
      <div class="ab-hero__glow"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="ab-stat-grid">
      <div class="ab-stat">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-passport"></i>
        <span class="ab-stat__num">4</span>
        <span class="ab-stat__label">Core Programs</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-stat ab-stat--accent">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-plane-departure"></i>
        <span class="ab-stat__flag">🇮🇳 → 🇩🇪</span>
        <span class="ab-stat__label">India to Germany</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-stat">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-filter"></i>
        <span class="ab-stat__num">5</span>
        <span class="ab-stat__label">Stage Vetting</span>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-stat">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-building-user"></i>
        <span class="ab-stat__num">15+</span>
        <span class="ab-stat__label">Industries Served</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="ab-tri-flags">
      <div class="ab-flag-node ab-flag-node--se">
        <span>🇸🇪</span>
        <small>Sweden HQ</small>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-flag-node ab-flag-node--in">
        <span>🇮🇳</span>
        <small>India Network</small>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-flag-node ab-flag-node--de">
        <span>🇩🇪</span>
        <small>Germany Focus</small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  WHO WE ARE — Wide typography-led section
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="who-we-are">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="wwa__inner">
      <aside class="wwa__sidebar">
        <span class="section-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-book-open"></i> Our Story</span>
        <h2>A Tri-Country <span class="text-gradient">Workforce Bridge</span></h2>
        <div class="wwa__sidebar-cards">
          <div class="wwa__country-card">
            <div class="wwa__country-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-map-location-dot"></i></div>
            <h4>Headquartered in Sweden</h4>
            <p>Operating with Scandinavian precision and access to Nordic and German labor markets.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="wwa__country-card wwa__country-card--featured">
            <div class="wwa__country-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-building-flag"></i></div>
            <h4>Germany-Focused Operations</h4>
            <p>Deep expertise in German labor law, visa pathways, and workforce integration.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="wwa__country-card">
            <div class="wwa__country-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-handshake-simple"></i></div>
            <h4>India Talent Alliance</h4>
            <p>Institutional partnerships providing access to a wide, qualified Indian candidate pool.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>

      <div class="wwa__text">
        <p class="wwa__text-large">Scandic Roots was founded with a single clear vision — to solve Germany's accelerating skilled-labor shortage through a process-driven, ethical, and deeply personal approach to international recruitment.</p>
        <p>Headquartered in Sweden, with deep operational roots both in India and Germany, we bring a uniquely multi-jurisdictional perspective to workforce solutions. Our team understands the nuances of German labor law, the complexities of Indian educational credentials, and the cultural integration required for long-term placement success.</p>
        <p>We support four key pathways: the <strong>German Opportunity Card (Chancenkarte)</strong> for self-directed job seekers, <strong>Indian Nurses Recruitment</strong> for Germany's healthcare sector, <strong>Ausbildung Placement</strong> for vocational trainees, and <strong>International Skilled Worker Recruitment</strong> for industrial and technical employers.</p>
        <div class="wwa__divider"></div>
        <div class="wwa__bullets">
          <div class="wwa__bullet"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i><span>No hidden fees for candidates — full transparency, always.</span></div>
          <div class="wwa__bullet"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i><span>Full compliance with German and EU recruitment standards.</span></div>
          <div class="wwa__bullet"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i><span>Post-placement support until successful long-term integration.</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  MISSION & VALUES — Dark card masonry grid
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="values-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="values-section__header">
      <span class="section-badge section-badge--light"><i class="fa-solid fa-gem"></i> What Drives Us</span>
      <h2>Our Mission <span class="text-gradient-light">&amp; Core Values</span></h2>
      <p>Every decision we make is guided by these principles — from sourcing our first candidate to supporting integration years after placement.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="values-masonry">
      <div class="val-card val-card--big">
        <div class="val-card__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye"></i></div>
        <h3>Our Mission</h3>
        <p>To provide German employers with reliable, professionally screened, and language-prepared candidates from India who can integrate efficiently and contribute to long-term workforce development — while giving Indian professionals a structured, ethical pathway to a better future in Germany.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="val-card">
        <div class="val-card__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass-chart"></i></div>
        <h3>Precision Matching</h3>
        <p>Every candidate is evaluated for technical skill, language proficiency, cultural fit, and compliance.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="val-card">
        <div class="val-card__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-scale-balanced"></i></div>
        <h3>Ethical Recruitment</h3>
        <p>Full transparency. No hidden fees. No shortcuts in compliance. German and EU standards, always.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="val-card val-card--accent">
        <div class="val-card__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-earth-europe"></i></div>
        <h3>Cultural Integration</h3>
        <p>We prepare candidates not just for employment, but for life in Germany — workplace culture, European social norms, and day-to-day regulations.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="val-card">
        <div class="val-card__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-handshake-angle"></i></div>
        <h3>Long-Term Commitment</h3>
        <p>We don't stop at placement. Post-arrival support, orientation classes, and follow-up ensure retention.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="val-card">
        <div class="val-card__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i></div>
        <h3>Workforce Continuity</h3>
        <p>We build long-term talent pipelines — not one-off placements — for sustainable workforce stability.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  FOUR PROGRAMS — Horizontal scroll cards
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="programs-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="programs-section__header">
      <span class="section-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-briefcase"></i> What We Offer</span>
      <h2>Our Four <span class="text-gradient">Core Programs</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="prog-tracks">
      <div class="prog-track">
        <div class="prog-track__num">01</div>
        <div class="prog-track__icon-wrap">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-passport"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Opportunity Card <br /><span>(Chancenkarte)</span></h3>
        <p>Points-based residence permit for non-EU professionals to search for employment in Germany for up to 12 months without a prior job offer.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Language proficiency assessment</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Sperrkonto support (€12,000+)</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Document preparation guidance</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Post-arrival job search orientation</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services#opportunity">Learn More <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-track prog-track--featured">
        <div class="prog-track__num">02</div>
        <div class="prog-track__icon-wrap">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-user-nurse"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Nurses to the<br /><span>German Healthcare System</span></h3>
        <p>Well-qualified, experienced, and B1–B2 German language-skilled Indian nurses for hospitals, elderly care centers, and rehabilitation facilities across Germany.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> B1–B2 German proficiency</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Recognized Diploma/Bachelor's in Nursing</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Qualification recognition support</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Integration & relocation assistance</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services#nurses">Learn More <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-track">
        <div class="prog-track__num">03</div>
        <div class="prog-track__icon-wrap">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-graduation-cap"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>Ausbildung<br /><span>Candidate Placement</span></h3>
        <p>Motivated Indian candidates for Germany's dual vocational training system — pre-screened, A2–B1 German-language prepared, and integration-ready.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Sector-specific matching</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> August–September & Feb–March intakes</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Relocation support</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> European social orientation</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services#ausbildung">Learn More <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>

      <div class="prog-track">
        <div class="prog-track__num">04</div>
        <div class="prog-track__icon-wrap">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-helmet-safety"></i>
        </div>
        <h3>International Skilled<br /><span>Workers Recruitment</span></h3>
        <p>Experienced workers for Germany's shipbuilding, meat processing, and industrial sectors — language-prepared and pre-screened for immediate integration.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Shipbuilding & welding experts</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Meat processing professionals</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> Industrial & logistics workers</li>
          <li><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i> A2–B1 German preparation</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/services#skilled">Learn More <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  INDIA TRAINING ALLIANCE — Full-width dark section with cards
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="training-alliance">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="training-alliance__header">
      <span class="section-badge section-badge--light"><i class="fa-solid fa-school-flag"></i> India Alliance</span>
      <h2>In-House <span class="text-gradient-light">Training Facility</span></h2>
      <p>Through institutional partnerships across India, we operate a comprehensive pre-departure facility that prepares candidates for life and work in Germany — before they ever board a flight.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ta-cards">
      <div class="ta-card ta-card--featured">
        <div class="ta-card__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-comments"></i></div>
        <h3>German Language Training</h3>
        <p>Conducted by <strong>native German speakers</strong>. Our language training goes beyond classroom basics — candidates learn workplace German, industry-specific vocabulary, everyday communication, and social skills, structured to A1–B2 levels depending on the program.</p>
        <div class="ta-levels">
          <span>A1</span><span>A2</span><span>B1</span><span>B2</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="ta-card">
        <div class="ta-card__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-microphone-lines"></i></div>
        <h3>Interview Preparation</h3>
        <p>Mock interview sessions simulating actual German employer environments, technical questions, and professional presentation in German.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ta-card">
        <div class="ta-card__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-gavel"></i></div>
        <h3>German Laws & Regulations</h3>
        <p>Labor law basics, social insurance, workplace safety regulations, and housing laws relevant to newcomers in Germany.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ta-card">
        <div class="ta-card__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-people-arrows"></i></div>
        <h3>European Social & Cultural Norms</h3>
        <p>Orientation sessions on social etiquette, punctuality, hierarchy, public transport and integration into German community life.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ta-card">
        <div class="ta-card__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-briefcase"></i></div>
        <h3>Workplace Culture Readiness</h3>
        <p>German workplace values — efficiency, precision, indirect communication, professional boundaries — to reduce cultural shock and accelerate integration.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ta-card">
        <div class="ta-card__icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-clipboard-check"></i></div>
        <h3>Document & Compliance Prep</h3>
        <p>Guided preparation of academic transcripts, certificates, police clearance, health records, Sperrkonto, and visa applications.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ta-pullquote">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left"></i>
      <blockquote>Most agencies simply forward CVs.<br /><strong>We build candidates.</strong></blockquote>
      <cite>— Scandic Roots Training Philosophy</cite>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  5-STAGE VETTING — Alternating zigzag timeline
═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="vetting-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="vetting-section__header">
      <span class="section-badge"><i class="fa-solid fa-filter"></i> Our Vetting Process</span>
      <h2>How We <span class="text-gradient">Select Candidates</span></h2>
      <p>Our 5-stage screening process is one of the most rigorous in the industry — ensuring every candidate we present is genuinely qualified and fully compliant.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="vet-timeline">
      <div class="vet-item">
        <div class="vet-item__connector-wrap">
          <div class="vet-step"><i class="fa-solid fa-language"></i></div>
          <div class="vet-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="vet-content vet-content--right">
          <span class="vet-num">01</span>
          <h3>Language Proficiency Check</h3>
          <p>Structured face-to-face or video German language interviews. Candidates are assessed across spoken fluency, comprehension, writing ability, and context-specific vocabulary. Minimum requirements set by program type (A1 for Chancenkarte; A2–B1 for Ausbildung and Skilled Workers).</p>
          <div class="vet-tags">
            <span>Spoken Interview</span><span>Written Test</span><span>Level Certification</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="vet-item vet-item--flip">
        <div class="vet-content vet-content--left">
          <span class="vet-num">02</span>
          <h3>Educational Document Verification</h3>
          <p>All educational and vocational credentials are collected and cross-verified. We assess whether qualifications are recognized under German and EU frameworks, check for equivalency, and identify any gaps requiring additional certification.</p>
          <div class="vet-tags">
            <span>Degree Verification</span><span>Vocational Credentials</span><span>Experience Letters</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="vet-item__connector-wrap">
          <div class="vet-step"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-contract"></i></div>
          <div class="vet-line"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="vet-item">
        <div class="vet-item__connector-wrap">
          <div class="vet-step vet-step--dark"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
          <div class="vet-line"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="vet-content vet-content--right">
          <span class="vet-num">03</span>
          <h3>Criminal Record Check</h3>
          <p>Every candidate submits valid police clearance certificates from all countries of residence in the past 10 years. We carefully review documents and decline any candidate with a disqualifying record — protecting employers and ensuring placement integrity.</p>
          <div class="vet-tags">
            <span>Police Clearance</span><span>Background Screening</span><span>Zero Tolerance</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="vet-item vet-item--flip">
        <div class="vet-content vet-content--left">
          <span class="vet-num">04</span>
          <h3>Financial Credibility Review</h3>
          <p>For Chancenkarte applicants, we verify that candidates have or are opening a German blocked bank account (Sperrkonto) with the required balance (approximately €12,000+). We also assess overall financial credibility to ensure candidates can manage the transition period effectively.</p>
          <div class="vet-tags">
            <span>Sperrkonto Proof</span><span>Financial Statement</span><span>Self-Sufficiency Check</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="vet-item__connector-wrap">
          <div class="vet-step"><i class="fa-solid fa-wallet"></i></div>
          <div class="vet-line"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="vet-item">
        <div class="vet-item__connector-wrap">
          <div class="vet-step vet-step--final"><i class="fa-solid fa-thumbs-up"></i></div>
        </div>
        <div class="vet-content vet-content--right">
          <span class="vet-num">05</span>
          <h3>Eligibility & Compliance Final Sign-Off</h3>
          <p>Our compliance team conducts a final holistic review: immigration eligibility, points-system scoring (for Chancenkarte), visa pathway suitability, and employer-specific requirements. Only candidates who pass all five stages receive our formal recommendation to the employer.</p>
          <div class="vet-tags">
            <span>Points System Check</span><span>Immigration Review</span><span>Employer-Ready</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

